description:
Crucifixion of Jesus 
Maybe this eater you should think less about the chocolate and more about what Easter is really about! 
The story of jesus' death.
Oh, and remember to watch is HD!

Wow, 13,700 views in a year thats big for me!

Tell me if you think it would be good if I made a re-masted version with my new set up.
